# Responsive Login Page 
 This project is a responsive login page created using HTML and CSS.
 The login page adapts to different screen sizes, providing an optimal viewing experience across various devices.

## Features
    - Responsive design 
    - Centered login form 
    - Input fields for username and password
    - login button 
    - Background image 
    - Modern CSS styling 

## Technologies Used
- HTML 
-CSS

## Link to preview:https://sowmya-1313.github.io/Login-page/
